    "Overall, Topic 1 review findings is consistent with the study of Jelodar et al. (2019) that found LDA as the most popular TM method.",
    "Our findings further suggest BTM and NTM are also popular methods, however, the use of BERT embeddings for TM is producing SOTA results in recent times.",
    "Similarly, TM has been applied to various domain like financial news (García-Méndez et al. 2023; Katarya et al. 2022), Chinese web news (Sun et al. 2011), airline customer reviews (Srinivas and Ramachandiran 2024), banking (Ogunleye et al. 2023) and news articles (Altuncu et al. 2021).",
    "Moreover, the papers reviewed shows TM algorithms were used to enhance the performance of other tasks, specifically, genomic sequence classification.",
    "For illustration, La- Rosa et al. (2015) employed LDA to extract topics from nucleotide Literature review synthesis sequences corpus, and thereafter used the topic labels to classify DNA sequence document."
